        <div class="row-a">
            <div class="column double">
                <article class="w112 "
             data-section="opinion_columnists_ianodoherty" data-domain="www.independent.ie">
        <script type='text/javascript' src='//assets.kampyle.com/clients/1755186/d/k_config.js'></script><h1>O'Doherty: US abortion scandal will cause ripple here too</h1>
    <h2></h2><script type='text/javascript' src='//assets.kampyle.com/clients/1755186/d/k_config.js'></script><section class="body ">
            <div class="w info" data-widget="Redesign Article Page tools Widget">
    <div class="author">
            <a href="http://www.independent.ie/opinion/independent-journalists/ian-odoherty/">
                                    <figure>
                                <img src="http://www.independent.ie/opinion/independent-journalists/article30415445.ece/f4538/ALTERNATES/w50square/Ian-ODoherty-bio.jpg" width="50" height="50" alt="" />
                            </figure></a>
                            <h3 class="hx">
                        <a href="http://www.independent.ie/opinion/independent-journalists/ian-odoherty/">Ian O'Doherty</a>
